WEBVTT

00:00:00.006 --> 00:01:00.006

00:01:30.220 --> 00:01:32.980
[Episode 02]

00:01:33.560 --> 00:01:34.840
Let me pay for the meal, okay?

00:01:35.200 --> 00:01:35.710
Alright, then.

00:01:35.870 --> 00:01:37.280
For Vice Mayor's sake.

00:01:39.070 --> 00:01:40.430
How do you know about my dad?

00:01:42.280 --> 00:01:43.680
I'm a Student Union officer.

00:01:43.710 --> 00:01:44.350
It's easy for me

00:01:44.350 --> 00:01:45.760
to check a student's background.

00:01:46.760 --> 00:01:47.430
Don't blame me.

00:01:47.870 --> 00:01:48.680
I had no choice.

00:01:49.230 --> 00:01:50.840
You made yourself sound pretty innocent.

00:01:52.480 --> 00:01:53.120
Actually,

00:01:53.480 --> 00:01:54.230
I've heard the name

00:01:54.230 --> 00:01:55.430
Meng Siyuan at home.

00:01:56.000 --> 00:01:56.920
My dad said your dad

00:01:56.920 --> 00:01:58.430
is the most promising young official

00:01:58.640 --> 00:01:59.480
in the province.

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:01.760
Why would your dad mention my dad?

00:02:03.070 --> 00:02:04.430
Well, not to me, of course.

00:02:05.070 --> 00:02:06.230
I heard it when he was talking

00:02:06.230 --> 00:02:06.870
with some

00:02:07.000 --> 00:02:07.680
officials at home.

00:02:12.120 --> 00:02:13.400
Here, try this.

00:02:14.190 --> 00:02:14.840
Thanks.

00:02:15.360 --> 00:02:16.080
To be honest,

00:02:17.030 --> 00:02:18.310
with a family like mine,

00:02:18.470 --> 00:02:19.470
I need to be very cautious

00:02:19.680 --> 00:02:20.680
about choosing a girlfriend.

00:02:21.190 --> 00:02:22.120
If we knew nothing

00:02:22.120 --> 00:02:23.120
about your background,

00:02:23.400 --> 00:02:24.710
my parents wouldn't agree.

00:02:25.430 --> 00:02:25.960
So,

00:02:26.120 --> 00:02:27.120
you really can't blame me.

00:02:31.240 --> 00:02:32.150
I read your article.

00:02:32.280 --> 00:02:33.560
I know your family is very strict.

00:02:34.190 --> 00:02:35.630
To be your boyfriend,

00:02:35.800 --> 00:02:36.800
do I need your mom

00:02:36.800 --> 00:02:37.870
and dad's approval?

00:02:39.190 --> 00:02:39.710
Of course...

00:02:41.630 --> 00:02:42.280
Not.

00:02:43.870 --> 00:02:44.680
They don't interfere

00:02:44.680 --> 00:02:45.470
with my business.

00:03:14.280 --> 00:03:15.080
He's not reliable.

00:03:16.000 --> 00:03:16.590
Who?

00:03:17.360 --> 00:03:17.910
Han Bin.

00:03:19.630 --> 00:03:20.630
And why is that?

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:24.080
He had girlfriends before.

00:03:24.710 --> 00:03:25.360
More than one.

00:03:25.960 --> 00:03:27.080
He has such a good background.

00:03:27.240 --> 00:03:28.520
It would be strange

00:03:28.870 --> 00:03:30.310
if he'd never had any girlfriends.

00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:34.190
Just focus on yourself.

00:03:34.400 --> 00:03:35.560
If you can't find a girlfriend,

00:03:35.750 --> 00:03:36.870
I won't set you up with one.

00:03:46.190 --> 00:03:47.400
Time for you to go again.

00:03:47.680 --> 00:03:48.960
I can't bear to part with you.

00:03:50.240 --> 00:03:51.430
Ten more minutes, then.

00:03:52.560 --> 00:03:53.800
But the dorm might be locked.

00:03:54.430 --> 00:03:56.240
My friend lives on
the first floor of the dorm.

00:03:56.630 --> 00:03:57.870
She jumped in through the window.

00:04:02.630 --> 00:04:03.280
Fang Wanzhi!

00:04:03.560 --> 00:04:04.190
Fang Wanzhi!

00:04:05.120 --> 00:04:06.560
Your dad called. It's urgent.

00:04:07.680 --> 00:04:08.560
Miss, wait!

00:04:14.120 --> 00:04:15.560
You finally called me...

00:04:25.870 --> 00:04:26.560
What's going on?

00:04:26.800 --> 00:04:28.270
My mom's sick, vomiting blood.

00:04:28.510 --> 00:04:29.310
I need to go back.

00:04:29.630 --> 00:04:30.750
There are no trains at this time.

00:04:30.830 --> 00:04:32.190
I'll go to the station now and take

00:04:32.390 --> 00:04:33.390
the earliest train tomorrow.

00:04:33.510 --> 00:04:34.040
Wanzhi,

00:04:34.120 --> 00:04:34.800
I'll get your brother

00:04:34.800 --> 00:04:35.480
to go with you.

00:04:35.800 --> 00:04:36.920
Why tell him?

00:04:37.000 --> 00:04:38.040
He's not her real brother.

00:04:38.310 --> 00:04:39.040
Besides,

00:04:39.240 --> 00:04:39.950
even with him,

00:04:39.950 --> 00:04:40.680
you can't sleep in

00:04:40.680 --> 00:04:41.310
the train station!

00:04:43.160 --> 00:04:43.630
Listen,

00:04:43.950 --> 00:04:44.920
I'll call my brother's driver.

00:04:45.040 --> 00:04:46.120
We'll be there in four hours.

00:04:46.750 --> 00:04:47.630
That's not appropriate.

00:04:47.800 --> 00:04:48.630
Why not?

00:04:48.800 --> 00:04:49.560
I'll go with you

00:04:49.600 --> 00:04:50.510
to visit your mother.

00:05:02.510 --> 00:05:03.040
Dad!

00:05:03.360 --> 00:05:04.000
Mr. Xiao...

00:05:04.070 --> 00:05:04.680
Wanzhi.

00:05:05.950 --> 00:05:07.000
What happened to Mom?

00:05:07.240 --> 00:05:07.750
Stomach...

00:05:09.390 --> 00:05:10.310
It's her stomach.

00:05:12.190 --> 00:05:13.360
How come you're back so quickly?

00:05:13.480 --> 00:05:14.480
Which train did you take?

00:05:14.870 --> 00:05:15.430
Wanzhi?

00:05:17.430 --> 00:05:18.600
My classmate drove me back.

00:05:19.070 --> 00:05:19.600
Han Bin,

00:05:19.750 --> 00:05:20.480
this is my dad.

00:05:21.240 --> 00:05:21.920
Hello, Mr. Meng.

00:05:22.120 --> 00:05:22.830
I'm Han Bin.

00:05:26.680 --> 00:05:28.070
Why did Ms. Fang suddenly fall ill?

00:05:29.000 --> 00:05:30.160
Your mom's waiting for you.

00:05:51.920 --> 00:05:52.510
Mom...

00:05:56.480 --> 00:05:57.390
Wanzhi.

00:05:58.600 --> 00:06:01.430
Mom, I heard you vomited blood earlier.

00:06:03.000 --> 00:06:04.480
Don't scare me.

00:06:05.070 --> 00:06:05.750
The medical care

00:06:05.750 --> 00:06:06.950
here isn't good.

00:06:07.360 --> 00:06:08.310
Let's go to a bigger city.

00:06:08.480 --> 00:06:09.750
Maybe the capital.

00:06:10.000 --> 00:06:10.870
Han Bin told me

00:06:11.310 --> 00:06:12.390
his family has connections.

00:06:12.560 --> 00:06:13.120
They can find

00:06:13.120 --> 00:06:14.480
the best hospital and doctors.

00:06:14.800 --> 00:06:17.070
Who says the medical care in Jianglin

00:06:17.070 --> 00:06:17.830
is poor?

00:06:18.430 --> 00:06:19.630
This hospital's director

00:06:20.430 --> 00:06:21.240
and department heads

00:06:21.830 --> 00:06:23.390
are all my old classmates.

00:06:24.630 --> 00:06:26.000
Most of the nurses here

00:06:26.160 --> 00:06:27.630
were my students.

00:06:34.800 --> 00:06:36.070
Who is Han Bin?

00:06:37.920 --> 00:06:39.070
My classmate.

00:06:40.430 --> 00:06:41.360
He's a senior...

00:06:43.240 --> 00:06:44.390
And my boyfriend.

00:06:48.240 --> 00:06:49.800
He took me back home.

00:06:50.190 --> 00:06:51.950
I'll go bring him to see you.

00:06:53.240 --> 00:06:53.920
Okay.

00:07:00.750 --> 00:07:01.560
Where's Han Bin?

00:07:02.430 --> 00:07:03.240
Mr. Xiao sent him

00:07:03.240 --> 00:07:04.600
to rest at the hotel.

00:07:05.240 --> 00:07:06.680
Didn't he want to visit my mom?

00:07:06.720 --> 00:07:07.560
Why did he leave?

00:07:07.870 --> 00:07:08.920
He wanted to.

00:07:09.040 --> 00:07:09.830
But I refused.

00:07:10.870 --> 00:07:11.510
Why?

00:07:11.720 --> 00:07:12.390
It wasn't necessary.

00:07:14.870 --> 00:07:15.560
Wanzhi,

00:07:16.600 --> 00:07:17.800
since I went to work in the city,

00:07:17.800 --> 00:07:18.430
I've been busy.

00:07:19.070 --> 00:07:20.270
I haven't cared enough for you.

00:07:20.430 --> 00:07:20.950
I didn't even

00:07:20.950 --> 00:07:22.310
call you on your birthday.

00:07:22.920 --> 00:07:23.600
I'm sorry.

00:07:23.830 --> 00:07:24.360
Still, I have

00:07:24.360 --> 00:07:25.630
to remind you.

00:07:26.070 --> 00:07:27.480
Be careful with your relationship.

00:07:28.680 --> 00:07:29.310
That boy, Han Bin,

00:07:30.360 --> 00:07:31.190
doesn't suit you.

00:07:31.750 --> 00:07:33.270
And why is that?

00:07:33.800 --> 00:07:35.190
You don't even know him.

00:07:35.920 --> 00:07:36.720
Besides,

00:07:36.870 --> 00:07:38.680
he drove me back at midnight

00:07:38.830 --> 00:07:40.120
and wanted to visit Mom,

00:07:40.270 --> 00:07:42.160
but you just drove him away.

00:07:42.560 --> 00:07:43.870
How could you do that?

00:07:44.160 --> 00:07:45.630
I'm really upset right now.

00:07:45.630 --> 00:07:46.920
And your mom's still lying in bed.

00:07:47.040 --> 00:07:47.720
I can't explain it

00:07:47.720 --> 00:07:49.070
to you with just a few words.

00:07:49.390 --> 00:07:50.360
Just break up with him.

00:07:51.160 --> 00:07:51.920
I won't!

00:07:55.120 --> 00:07:55.870
This is the hospital.

00:07:55.870 --> 00:07:57.000
I don't want to argue with you.

00:07:57.240 --> 00:07:58.240
But I won't compromise

00:07:58.750 --> 00:07:59.430
on this because

00:07:59.430 --> 00:08:00.430
you're being willful.

00:08:00.800 --> 00:08:01.750
I'll say it again.

00:08:02.480 --> 00:08:03.160
Han Bin...

00:08:04.190 --> 00:08:05.270
You must break up with him.

00:08:26.270 --> 00:08:27.240
Hey, Han Bin.

00:08:27.870 --> 00:08:28.390
It's me.

00:08:29.070 --> 00:08:29.950
I'm sorry.

00:08:30.600 --> 00:08:31.480
Today, my dad...

00:08:31.510 --> 00:08:32.550
I totally understand

00:08:32.550 --> 00:08:33.440
how he feels.

00:08:33.870 --> 00:08:34.510
It's also my bad.

00:08:34.600 --> 00:08:35.480
I came at a bad time.

00:08:36.600 --> 00:08:37.550
I'll head back tomorrow.

00:08:37.870 --> 00:08:38.750
Take care of your mom.

00:08:38.870 --> 00:08:40.150
I'll ask for leave on your behalf.

00:08:42.080 --> 00:08:42.630
Alright.

00:08:43.630 --> 00:08:44.480
Thank you.

00:08:59.240 --> 00:09:00.000
Your mom wants you.

00:09:09.240 --> 00:09:10.550
Are you upset with your dad?

00:09:12.510 --> 00:09:13.200
No.

00:09:13.960 --> 00:09:16.030
It shows on your face.

00:09:18.200 --> 00:09:19.790
Your dad is educated

00:09:20.080 --> 00:09:21.120
and has experienced

00:09:21.120 --> 00:09:22.200
many ups and downs.

00:09:24.320 --> 00:09:25.750
You should ask for his opinion

00:09:26.630 --> 00:09:28.120
when you encounter problems.

00:09:28.480 --> 00:09:30.030
But what if he's wrong?

00:09:30.750 --> 00:09:32.390
And you said you weren't upset?

00:09:33.270 --> 00:09:34.630
He drove Han Bin away

00:09:34.910 --> 00:09:36.030
for no reason.

00:09:37.000 --> 00:09:38.670
I was so embarrassed.

00:09:39.910 --> 00:09:40.910
He must have

00:09:41.480 --> 00:09:42.870
his own reasons.

00:09:44.240 --> 00:09:46.150
In the future, I won't be able to help

00:09:48.000 --> 00:09:49.550
if you argue with your dad.

00:09:51.200 --> 00:09:52.720
Don't say that.

00:09:53.870 --> 00:09:55.550
Please don't say it like that.

00:09:56.600 --> 00:09:57.360
Don't cry.

00:09:59.270 --> 00:10:00.510
Stop crying now.

00:10:03.670 --> 00:10:04.390
If you don't,

00:10:05.120 --> 00:10:06.270
the nurse will come.

00:10:08.720 --> 00:10:10.480
I wrote you a letter.

00:10:11.080 --> 00:10:12.390
I handed it to your dad.

00:10:13.720 --> 00:10:15.790
It's very important for you.

00:10:17.960 --> 00:10:18.960
After reading it,

00:10:19.960 --> 00:10:21.360
you'll understand.

00:10:22.150 --> 00:10:23.200
I won't read it!

00:10:23.550 --> 00:10:24.790
I won't!

00:10:25.440 --> 00:10:26.600
Don't worry, Wanzhi.

00:10:27.870 --> 00:10:28.960
Though my illness

00:10:30.030 --> 00:10:31.630
runs in the family,

00:10:33.270 --> 00:10:34.960
it won't be passed on to you.

00:10:36.120 --> 00:10:38.360
Stop saying that!

00:10:42.670 --> 00:10:43.600
Here.

00:10:44.240 --> 00:10:45.720
It's for you.

00:10:47.320 --> 00:10:48.240
What is it?

00:10:50.030 --> 00:10:51.550
Open it and read it.

00:11:02.000 --> 00:11:03.080
I wanted to sort it out first

00:11:03.080 --> 00:11:04.240
before giving it to you.

00:11:06.200 --> 00:11:06.790
But...

00:11:09.030 --> 00:11:10.240
You're grown up now.

00:11:10.720 --> 00:11:12.150
You'll have to go

00:11:12.630 --> 00:11:14.120
to the bank for these yourself.

00:11:14.240 --> 00:11:16.910
Stop saying that! I don't want to!

00:11:16.960 --> 00:11:18.480
I don't!

00:11:18.600 --> 00:11:19.440
Mom...

00:11:19.440 --> 00:11:20.390
I don't want it.

00:11:20.870 --> 00:11:23.080
Please don't say that!

00:12:30.200 --> 00:12:30.750
Wanzhi,

00:12:31.750 --> 00:12:32.670
I came back late.

00:12:33.750 --> 00:12:35.440
I didn't get to see
your mom one last time.

00:12:36.390 --> 00:12:37.150
I'm sorry.

00:13:04.030 --> 00:13:04.790
Wanzhi,

00:13:07.200 --> 00:13:09.080
you haven't talked
to your dad for three days.

00:13:09.790 --> 00:13:10.790
Your mother's gone.

00:13:11.440 --> 00:13:12.240
In this world,

00:13:12.910 --> 00:13:14.790
your dad is the one
who loves you the most.

00:13:15.000 --> 00:13:16.360
He's staying home today.

00:13:17.150 --> 00:13:18.750
You should hurry back

00:13:18.790 --> 00:13:19.870
and talk to him.

00:13:20.870 --> 00:13:21.790
There shouldn't be

00:13:21.910 --> 00:13:23.240
any grudges between you two

00:13:23.240 --> 00:13:24.200
as father and daughter.

00:13:27.910 --> 00:13:29.150
I understand how you feel.

00:13:31.910 --> 00:13:34.240
If Jingyu were still alive,
(Support Admin Watch on
kissasia.cam or kisskh.org)

00:13:35.120 --> 00:13:36.030
she'd understand

00:13:36.030 --> 00:13:37.080
how you feel as well.

00:13:38.270 --> 00:13:39.320
Now that it has

00:13:39.320 --> 00:13:40.440
already happened,

00:13:41.630 --> 00:13:43.000
life must go on.

00:13:46.240 --> 00:13:46.840
Alright.

00:13:53.630 --> 00:13:54.320
Mrs. Li...

00:13:56.360 --> 00:13:56.960
She is...

00:14:00.440 --> 00:14:01.120
Wanzhi!

00:14:01.870 --> 00:14:02.510
Wanzhi?

00:14:03.550 --> 00:14:04.270
Wanzhi?

00:14:08.600 --> 00:14:09.270
Wanzhi,

00:14:09.790 --> 00:14:11.360
I'm your mother's good friend.

00:14:12.030 --> 00:14:13.320
Your mother is gone now.

00:14:14.030 --> 00:14:14.790
From now on,

00:14:15.120 --> 00:14:17.030
just tell me if you need anything.

00:14:17.550 --> 00:14:18.750
I'll take care of you

00:14:18.750 --> 00:14:19.720
as your mother did.

00:14:33.150 --> 00:14:33.790
Wanzhi?

00:14:35.000 --> 00:14:35.750
Wanzhi?

00:14:43.360 --> 00:14:44.480
This separate burial plot

00:14:44.870 --> 00:14:47.030
was specially approved
by the government because

00:14:47.840 --> 00:14:48.670
of the Fang family

00:14:48.750 --> 00:14:50.080
and your mother's exceptional

00:14:51.030 --> 00:14:52.080
contributions to Yu County.

00:14:53.720 --> 00:14:54.670
This photo

00:14:55.960 --> 00:14:57.390
and the words on it

00:14:58.790 --> 00:14:59.790
were chosen by your mom

00:14:59.790 --> 00:15:00.840
when she was alive.

00:15:02.840 --> 00:15:04.150
Because I work for the government,

00:15:05.150 --> 00:15:06.750
and she worried this grave

00:15:07.600 --> 00:15:08.670
would raise suspicion

00:15:08.670 --> 00:15:09.630
about me,

00:15:10.440 --> 00:15:11.360
she insisted on

00:15:11.360 --> 00:15:12.910
not putting my name on it.

00:15:15.600 --> 00:15:17.320
And that's what I did.

00:15:22.030 --> 00:15:23.670
She's buried now.

00:15:24.390 --> 00:15:25.670
And everything's settled.

00:15:27.360 --> 00:15:29.240
You've done your part in this.

00:15:30.670 --> 00:15:32.080
Go back to school.

00:15:32.790 --> 00:15:33.750
Focus on your studies.

00:15:36.630 --> 00:15:37.600
Your mom wanted you to pursue

00:15:37.600 --> 00:15:38.510
further education,

00:15:39.510 --> 00:15:40.960
ideally a doctorate,

00:15:41.960 --> 00:15:42.630
and make a greater

00:15:42.630 --> 00:15:43.840
contribution to Yu County

00:15:44.720 --> 00:15:46.910
like the Fang family's ancestors.

00:15:47.840 --> 00:15:49.000
Focus on yourself first.

00:15:55.550 --> 00:15:56.630
You must let me explain

00:15:57.790 --> 00:15:59.360
what happened that day.

00:16:00.750 --> 00:16:01.790
You should know

00:16:02.200 --> 00:16:03.630
that Mrs. Li and her husband

00:16:04.240 --> 00:16:06.080
were your mom's and my best friends.

00:16:06.840 --> 00:16:07.720
But the day

00:16:07.720 --> 00:16:08.960
before your mother passed away,

00:16:10.360 --> 00:16:11.750
she also lost her husband

00:16:13.080 --> 00:16:14.080
in a car accident.

00:16:14.670 --> 00:16:16.550
At such a difficult time,

00:16:17.200 --> 00:16:18.120
I couldn't attend

00:16:18.120 --> 00:16:19.600
her husband's funeral,

00:16:20.320 --> 00:16:21.320
and she couldn't attend

00:16:21.320 --> 00:16:22.270
your mom's funeral, either.

00:16:23.480 --> 00:16:24.750
That's why she was so sad

00:16:26.150 --> 00:16:27.390
the last time we met.

00:16:28.510 --> 00:16:29.550
What I'm trying to say

00:16:33.320 --> 00:16:34.390
is that we're old friends,

00:16:34.390 --> 00:16:35.320
and we've been very

00:16:36.200 --> 00:16:37.150
good friends for years.

00:16:37.200 --> 00:16:38.150
Stop it.

00:16:40.150 --> 00:16:40.840
No need.

00:16:53.150 --> 00:16:53.910
Give me the letter.

00:16:56.630 --> 00:16:57.390
What letter?

00:16:57.840 --> 00:16:59.320
The letter Mom left me.

00:17:01.080 --> 00:17:02.600
I don't know what you're talking about.

00:17:03.630 --> 00:17:05.030
Mom told me herself that

00:17:05.160 --> 00:17:06.030
she handed it to you.

00:17:07.240 --> 00:17:08.110
Even if she did,

00:17:10.070 --> 00:17:10.750
as you know,

00:17:12.110 --> 00:17:13.480
I've been busy these days.

00:17:14.030 --> 00:17:14.880
I've been handling

00:17:14.880 --> 00:17:15.830
your mother's funeral.

00:17:17.750 --> 00:17:18.400
Maybe I...

00:17:18.480 --> 00:17:19.400
Maybe I just forgot.

00:17:19.750 --> 00:17:22.160
What do you mean you just forgot?

00:17:22.920 --> 00:17:24.160
You forgot such

00:17:24.160 --> 00:17:25.550
an important letter?

00:17:26.070 --> 00:17:26.830
Give it to me!

00:17:27.550 --> 00:17:28.510
Oh, you...

00:17:28.880 --> 00:17:30.440
You haven't talked to me for days.

00:17:30.440 --> 00:17:31.200
And now you ask me

00:17:31.200 --> 00:17:31.960
for that letter?

00:17:32.000 --> 00:17:32.720
Am I wrong?

00:17:32.720 --> 00:17:33.750
Those were Mom's last words

00:17:33.750 --> 00:17:34.720
to me before she passed away!

00:17:34.960 --> 00:17:36.240
And you just forgot it so easily?

00:17:36.240 --> 00:17:37.510
How could you do this to her?

00:17:46.480 --> 00:17:47.750
You lost your mother,

00:17:49.790 --> 00:17:51.070
and I lost my love.

00:17:52.550 --> 00:17:53.750
Actually, our grief

00:17:53.750 --> 00:17:54.590
is the same.

00:17:55.480 --> 00:17:56.270
Why can't you...

00:17:57.160 --> 00:17:57.920
Why can't you

00:17:57.920 --> 00:17:59.160
show me some understanding?

00:17:59.680 --> 00:18:00.270
I...

00:18:33.550 --> 00:18:34.110
Wan...

00:18:34.790 --> 00:18:35.510
Wanzhi.

00:18:35.680 --> 00:18:36.200
You...

00:18:37.960 --> 00:18:39.270
I'll find the letter myself.

00:18:39.790 --> 00:18:40.750
Your dad must have his

00:18:40.750 --> 00:18:41.960
own reasons for keeping it.

00:18:42.160 --> 00:18:42.830
You... You...

00:18:43.400 --> 00:18:45.000
You're going too far!

00:18:45.510 --> 00:18:46.720
Grandma Yu,

00:18:47.880 --> 00:18:48.790
you've been favoring me.

00:18:48.790 --> 00:18:50.350
But why are you taking my dad's side?

00:18:53.830 --> 00:18:54.590
Don't cry.

00:18:55.030 --> 00:18:55.790
There, there...

00:19:06.200 --> 00:19:07.640
I'm so sorry for today, everyone,

00:19:08.110 --> 00:19:09.110
for making you all

00:19:09.510 --> 00:19:10.880
take me home first.

00:19:11.350 --> 00:19:12.160
Vice Mayor Meng,

00:19:12.920 --> 00:19:15.310
your house looks very grand!

00:19:15.400 --> 00:19:15.960
Exactly.

00:19:15.960 --> 00:19:17.640
This is my wife's family's house.

00:19:18.510 --> 00:19:19.750
The biggest regret today

00:19:20.160 --> 00:19:22.350
is that we didn't get
to toast to your wife.

00:19:23.510 --> 00:19:25.070
There will be chances.

00:19:25.550 --> 00:19:26.510
There always will be.

00:19:27.200 --> 00:19:27.750
Xiao,

00:19:28.200 --> 00:19:29.350
see the guests out for me.

00:19:30.350 --> 00:19:31.200
Everyone,

00:19:31.440 --> 00:19:32.070
please go back.

00:19:32.310 --> 00:19:32.790
Alright.

00:19:33.030 --> 00:19:33.400
Okay.

00:19:33.590 --> 00:19:34.550
Goodbye! Take care!

00:19:34.680 --> 00:19:35.200
Goodbye!

00:19:35.200 --> 00:19:35.510
Alright.

00:19:36.070 --> 00:19:36.480
Okay.

00:19:42.750 --> 00:19:43.440
Vice Mayor Meng?

00:19:44.270 --> 00:19:45.200
Did all the guests leave?

00:19:45.750 --> 00:19:46.240
Yes.

00:19:46.640 --> 00:19:47.310
-They left.
-Good...

00:19:49.720 --> 00:19:50.480
Hang in there.

00:19:50.720 --> 00:19:51.480
I'll go get Wanzhi.

00:19:52.880 --> 00:19:53.440
Xiao,

00:19:53.830 --> 00:19:54.440
don't do that.

00:19:54.880 --> 00:19:56.310
They must be asleep at this hour.

00:19:56.750 --> 00:19:58.160
I don't want Wanzhi to see this.

00:19:58.440 --> 00:19:59.640
I'll be fine after throwing up.

00:20:12.070 --> 00:20:13.070
You're both still up?

00:20:15.640 --> 00:20:16.590
I came back quite late.

00:20:17.550 --> 00:20:18.790
Sorry to disturb your rest.

00:20:18.920 --> 00:20:19.680
It's fine.

00:20:20.030 --> 00:20:22.000
You're a busy man with a big career.

00:20:22.240 --> 00:20:23.750
Socializing is part of your job.

00:20:24.030 --> 00:20:25.070
It's normal to disturb others.

00:20:25.400 --> 00:20:26.440
Wanzhi!

00:20:28.790 --> 00:20:29.590
Mr. Meng,

00:20:29.830 --> 00:20:30.880
let me cook you something.

00:20:31.640 --> 00:20:32.240
No need.

00:20:33.270 --> 00:20:34.000
Give me the letter.

00:20:39.880 --> 00:20:41.000
There is a letter.

00:20:42.160 --> 00:20:42.880
But I think

00:20:42.880 --> 00:20:44.920
it'd be better for you
to read the letter

00:20:45.400 --> 00:20:46.350
your mother left you

00:20:47.110 --> 00:20:48.070
after you start working,

00:20:48.640 --> 00:20:50.030
after you have a family,

00:20:50.750 --> 00:20:51.550
and after

00:20:51.550 --> 00:20:52.590
you become a mother

00:20:53.160 --> 00:20:53.790
yourself.

00:20:55.960 --> 00:20:56.920
Give it to me!

00:20:57.000 --> 00:20:58.590
Your dad's doing it for your own good.

00:20:58.590 --> 00:20:59.750
Grandma Yu, don't intervene.

00:20:59.750 --> 00:21:00.400
Back to your room!

00:21:00.510 --> 00:21:01.920
How can you talk to her like that?

00:21:02.110 --> 00:21:03.310
Fine, I'll go back to my room.

00:21:03.480 --> 00:21:04.920
Just don't fight.

00:21:07.680 --> 00:21:09.310
My mom left me that letter.

00:21:10.200 --> 00:21:10.960
I just don't get it.

00:21:10.960 --> 00:21:12.510
Why won't you give it to me?

00:21:13.070 --> 00:21:13.720
If you don't,

00:21:13.720 --> 00:21:14.400
I'll never

00:21:14.400 --> 00:21:15.110
come back again!

00:21:15.160 --> 00:21:15.750
Why don't you

00:21:15.750 --> 00:21:16.830
just cut ties with me, then?

00:21:16.830 --> 00:21:17.550
I can do that

00:21:17.550 --> 00:21:18.480
if you want to.

00:21:18.480 --> 00:21:18.960
You...

00:21:24.240 --> 00:21:24.790
Fine.

00:21:27.350 --> 00:21:28.270
Come with me.

00:22:25.350 --> 00:22:26.720
Read it in the study.

00:22:28.070 --> 00:22:28.830
Don't leave the room.

00:22:36.510 --> 00:22:37.350
(Wanzhi,)

00:22:37.790 --> 00:22:39.200
(my dear daughter.)

00:22:40.400 --> 00:22:42.550
(When you read this letter,)

00:22:43.270 --> 00:22:44.750
(I'm already long gone.)

00:22:46.240 --> 00:22:48.270
(I wanted to keep this)

00:22:48.920 --> 00:22:50.480
(a secret forever.)

00:22:51.480 --> 00:22:54.070
(But it'd be too selfish.)

00:22:57.400 --> 00:22:58.310
(Wanzhi,)

00:22:59.000 --> 00:23:00.590
(you must believe)

00:23:01.400 --> 00:23:02.400
(that your dad and I)

00:23:02.960 --> 00:23:04.830
(treat you 100%)

00:23:04.960 --> 00:23:06.480
(as our own.)

00:23:07.110 --> 00:23:07.920
(After I'm gone,)

00:23:09.750 --> 00:23:10.960
(his love for you)

00:23:11.680 --> 00:23:13.550
(will only grow deeper.)

00:23:14.590 --> 00:23:15.960
(It's completely up to you)

00:23:16.070 --> 00:23:18.000
(how to handle your relationship)

00:23:18.070 --> 00:23:20.350
(with your family on Shenxian Peak)

00:23:21.440 --> 00:23:24.510
(and the family here in Yu County.)

00:23:25.160 --> 00:23:27.030
(Either birth parents)

00:23:27.880 --> 00:23:30.510
(or foster parents,)

00:23:31.790 --> 00:23:33.160
(all is fate.)

00:23:34.200 --> 00:23:35.960
(And what fate means)

00:23:36.550 --> 00:23:38.960
(is that no matter)

00:23:39.680 --> 00:23:41.680
(how it starts and ends,)

00:23:42.480 --> 00:23:45.030
(it all follows its natural course.)

00:23:45.550 --> 00:23:47.070
(It has nothing to do with morals.)

00:23:48.440 --> 00:23:50.070
(I'll stop here.)

00:23:51.310 --> 00:23:52.550
(I've run out of strength.)

00:23:53.440 --> 00:23:56.640
(Forever yours, Mom.)

00:24:13.200 --> 00:24:13.880
Wanzhi?

00:24:15.350 --> 00:24:16.000
Wanzhi!

00:24:16.640 --> 00:24:17.200
Wanzhi?

00:24:17.440 --> 00:24:18.070
Wanzhi?

00:24:41.110 --> 00:24:41.920
Wanzhi!

00:24:42.720 --> 00:24:43.590
You're awake.

00:24:45.310 --> 00:24:46.160
That's great.

00:24:46.640 --> 00:24:48.440
Your dad was by your side all night.

00:24:48.880 --> 00:24:50.160
But there's an emergency.

00:24:51.000 --> 00:24:52.640
He had to go back for a meeting.

00:24:53.310 --> 00:24:54.920
I'll give him a call right away.

00:24:57.550 --> 00:24:58.400
Grandma Yu...

00:25:00.070 --> 00:25:01.070
My letter...

00:25:01.680 --> 00:25:02.270
It's here.

00:25:11.240 --> 00:25:13.030
Your dad asked me to keep it for you

00:25:15.440 --> 00:25:17.110
in case you wake up and ask for it.

00:25:25.960 --> 00:25:26.720
Grandma Yu,

00:25:27.480 --> 00:25:29.350
you've been around since I was a child.

00:25:31.590 --> 00:25:33.310
Just tell me the truth.

00:25:34.400 --> 00:25:35.880
Is what's written

00:25:37.310 --> 00:25:38.400
in this letter true?

00:26:17.510 --> 00:26:18.160
Wanzhi,

00:26:19.480 --> 00:26:20.720
yesterday, Vice Mayor Meng

00:26:21.200 --> 00:26:22.310
was drinking with suppliers

00:26:22.310 --> 00:26:23.160
from all over the country.

00:26:28.400 --> 00:26:29.790
He didn't want to ruin their mood.

00:26:30.550 --> 00:26:31.550
So he specially asked us

00:26:32.310 --> 00:26:33.200
not to mention

00:26:33.200 --> 00:26:34.240
Ms. Fang's death.

00:26:34.680 --> 00:26:35.350
You know,

00:26:35.880 --> 00:26:37.070
he can't hold his liquor.

00:26:39.110 --> 00:26:40.310
To save money on the project,

00:26:41.510 --> 00:26:42.310
he really did

00:26:42.310 --> 00:26:43.110
his best yesterday.

00:26:45.960 --> 00:26:46.720
Project?

00:26:47.550 --> 00:26:48.440
What project?

00:26:49.000 --> 00:26:49.640
Wanzhi,

00:26:50.030 --> 00:26:51.400
you don't pay
attention to your dad.

00:26:51.960 --> 00:26:52.750
He's in charge of

00:26:53.110 --> 00:26:54.160
the Jing River Bridge project

00:26:54.160 --> 00:26:55.000
right now.

00:26:55.830 --> 00:26:57.590
That's one of the national key projects,

00:26:58.110 --> 00:26:58.830
a major one.

00:27:09.920 --> 00:27:11.350
You don't need to read it twice, do you?

00:27:12.720 --> 00:27:13.400
Yeah.

00:27:14.070 --> 00:27:15.640
It's written very clearly in the letter.

00:27:21.160 --> 00:27:22.510
I want to go to Shenxian Peak.

00:27:23.110 --> 00:27:24.070
Absolutely not!

00:27:24.680 --> 00:27:25.350
Why?

00:27:26.830 --> 00:27:27.960
Don't do anything foolish.

00:27:28.880 --> 00:27:29.550
Obviously,

00:27:29.830 --> 00:27:30.920
your mom's death

00:27:31.200 --> 00:27:32.480
is a huge loss to

00:27:32.480 --> 00:27:33.590
your dad's political career.

00:27:34.070 --> 00:27:35.000
You could even say

00:27:35.680 --> 00:27:36.510
it directly ruined

00:27:36.510 --> 00:27:37.640
his path to further promotion.

00:27:39.110 --> 00:27:40.350
Let me analyze it for you.

00:27:41.070 --> 00:27:41.960
Yu County Nursing School,

00:27:42.030 --> 00:27:43.750
three hospitals, and
two children's welfare homes

00:27:43.750 --> 00:27:44.960
in Jianglin and Yu County

00:27:45.240 --> 00:27:46.480
were all founded

00:27:46.480 --> 00:27:47.880
by the Fang family back then.

00:27:48.510 --> 00:27:49.720
And because of that,

00:27:50.200 --> 00:27:50.830
Vice Mayor Meng,

00:27:50.830 --> 00:27:51.750
as their son-in-law...

00:27:51.750 --> 00:27:52.350
Enough.

00:27:52.920 --> 00:27:53.920
Your analysis has

00:27:53.920 --> 00:27:54.830
nothing to do with me

00:27:54.830 --> 00:27:55.830
going to Shenxian Peak.

00:27:56.070 --> 00:27:57.310
Of course it does!

00:27:57.960 --> 00:27:58.750
Your dad is facing

00:27:58.750 --> 00:27:59.880
the double blow

00:28:00.030 --> 00:28:01.920
of losing his wife and his career.

00:28:02.030 --> 00:28:02.720
At this moment,

00:28:02.960 --> 00:28:04.160
you, his adopted daughter,

00:28:04.160 --> 00:28:05.680
are his only emotional support.

00:28:06.030 --> 00:28:07.830
You should properly comfort him

00:28:07.830 --> 00:28:08.750
and be there for him.

00:28:08.880 --> 00:28:10.310
But I only want to know

00:28:10.310 --> 00:28:11.550
where I came from

00:28:12.240 --> 00:28:13.640
and why I was abandoned.

00:28:14.030 --> 00:28:15.720
Why do you want to know that?

00:28:16.000 --> 00:28:17.480
It must have been because of poverty.

00:28:17.960 --> 00:28:19.030
But with such nice

00:28:19.030 --> 00:28:19.960
foster parents,

00:28:20.110 --> 00:28:21.590
you're truly blessed.

00:28:22.830 --> 00:28:24.510
Just go and apologize to your dad,

00:28:24.640 --> 00:28:25.440
burn this letter

00:28:25.440 --> 00:28:26.550
right in front of him,

00:28:27.000 --> 00:28:28.110
and promise never to go...

00:28:30.880 --> 00:28:31.790
Promise never to go

00:28:31.790 --> 00:28:32.680
to Shenxian Peak.

00:28:34.240 --> 00:28:35.480
I'm saying this for your own good.

00:28:38.720 --> 00:28:39.790
Going to Shenxian Peak?

00:28:40.550 --> 00:28:41.110
Fine.

00:28:41.350 --> 00:28:42.000
I'll go with you.

00:28:42.350 --> 00:28:43.000
I'll buy tickets

00:28:43.030 --> 00:28:44.510
at the train station tomorrow morning.

00:28:45.310 --> 00:28:46.350
You think I should go?

00:28:49.270 --> 00:28:50.640
Han Bin didn't want me to go.

00:28:51.270 --> 00:28:52.790
He even gave me many reasons.

00:28:58.030 --> 00:28:59.400
Just do whatever you want to do,

00:28:59.750 --> 00:29:00.960
and go wherever you want to go.

00:29:01.640 --> 00:29:02.720
Why do you need a reason?

00:29:04.160 --> 00:29:05.070
I'll go with you

00:29:05.510 --> 00:29:06.400
and protect you.

00:29:07.920 --> 00:29:08.880
You silly.

00:29:09.480 --> 00:29:10.750
I don't need your protection.

00:29:11.510 --> 00:29:12.200
Besides,

00:29:13.030 --> 00:29:14.440
I want to go alone this time.

00:29:16.000 --> 00:29:16.510
Fine.

00:29:16.830 --> 00:29:18.000
I'll go to the train station

00:29:18.480 --> 00:29:19.160
and buy a ticket.

00:30:38.310 --> 00:30:38.920
I'm a monster!

00:30:39.200 --> 00:30:39.830
I'm a monster!

00:30:47.350 --> 00:30:48.030
Why are you here?

00:30:49.440 --> 00:30:50.480
I'm Fang Wanzhi.

00:30:51.790 --> 00:30:52.440
I don't know you.

00:30:53.400 --> 00:30:54.830
You saved my life over a decade ago.

00:30:55.720 --> 00:30:57.400
You were gored by a startled goat.

00:30:59.750 --> 00:31:00.550
Oh, I remember.

00:31:01.480 --> 00:31:04.070
You were only this tall back then.

00:31:05.000 --> 00:31:06.510
You're Principal Fang's daughter.

00:31:08.750 --> 00:31:09.880
I only just found out

00:31:10.270 --> 00:31:12.350
that Fang Jingyu was my foster mother.

00:31:13.240 --> 00:31:14.680
My surname was supposed to be He.

00:31:21.550 --> 00:31:22.310
You won't admit it?

00:31:23.750 --> 00:31:24.880
What do you want me to admit?

00:31:28.480 --> 00:31:29.270
My sin?

00:31:39.160 --> 00:31:40.590
That's not what I mean.

00:31:41.920 --> 00:31:43.000
I just came to see...

00:31:44.790 --> 00:31:45.480
Where is she?

00:31:47.440 --> 00:31:48.110
Who?

00:31:48.920 --> 00:31:49.790
My mother.

00:31:51.640 --> 00:31:52.270
She's dead.

00:31:53.440 --> 00:31:54.310
Long gone.

00:31:57.240 --> 00:31:58.440
When you ditched me back then,

00:31:58.920 --> 00:31:59.680
my...

00:32:01.830 --> 00:32:03.350
Did she cry?

00:32:10.270 --> 00:32:12.640
It was sunny that day,

00:32:13.240 --> 00:32:16.160
but suddenly,
there was thunder and rain.

00:32:19.110 --> 00:32:20.590
I didn't hear her crying.

00:32:25.440 --> 00:32:26.350
But I think

00:32:27.400 --> 00:32:28.440
she must have cried.

00:32:29.240 --> 00:32:31.110
She was pregnant with you for so long.

00:32:32.310 --> 00:32:33.270
It must have been tough.

00:32:34.880 --> 00:32:36.200
But she didn't even get to hold you.

00:32:37.480 --> 00:32:38.880
How could she not be sad?

00:32:40.640 --> 00:32:41.400
What about you?

00:32:44.160 --> 00:32:45.030
Ditching me like that,

00:32:45.400 --> 00:32:46.160
have you regretted it?

00:32:58.750 --> 00:32:59.510
I haven't.

00:33:01.640 --> 00:33:02.880
I sent you to

00:33:03.200 --> 00:33:05.160
a good family in town.

00:33:06.030 --> 00:33:07.590
That couple was old.

00:33:08.160 --> 00:33:09.030
They were well-educated

00:33:09.510 --> 00:33:10.510
but had no children.

00:33:14.960 --> 00:33:17.070
I thought it through carefully.

00:33:17.070 --> 00:33:18.440
It was the best choice for you.

00:33:19.510 --> 00:33:20.640
When I came back,

00:33:21.030 --> 00:33:22.200
someone even asked me

00:33:22.960 --> 00:33:25.270
why I didn't trade you

00:33:25.880 --> 00:33:27.240
for two bags of sweet potatoes

00:33:27.590 --> 00:33:29.350
or a few dozen tiles.

00:33:29.480 --> 00:33:30.790
I got mad the moment I heard that.

00:33:30.960 --> 00:33:32.550
So I grabbed my shovel
and beat them up.

00:33:32.790 --> 00:33:34.030
If I sold my daughter like that,

00:33:34.240 --> 00:33:35.590
what would that make me?

00:34:09.800 --> 00:34:10.710
If you hate me,

00:34:12.440 --> 00:34:13.710
just beat me however you want.

00:34:14.630 --> 00:34:15.510
I won't dodge.

00:34:16.590 --> 00:34:17.960
Hit me all you want.

00:34:30.840 --> 00:34:32.440
Thank you for telling me the truth.

00:34:33.510 --> 00:34:34.280
You're right.

00:34:35.070 --> 00:34:36.110
Your abandoning me

00:34:36.550 --> 00:34:37.150
was actually

00:34:37.150 --> 00:34:38.400
a blessing for me.

00:34:39.190 --> 00:34:40.960
Thank you for your wise decision.

00:34:41.920 --> 00:34:43.630
Why do you put it like that?

00:34:44.590 --> 00:34:46.190
You might as well beat me up.

00:34:52.670 --> 00:34:54.190
I have two older sisters,

00:34:54.550 --> 00:34:54.880
right?

00:35:07.230 --> 00:35:08.000
Over there.

00:35:16.480 --> 00:35:17.150
Look.

00:35:18.320 --> 00:35:19.320
That's my eldest daughter.

00:35:21.360 --> 00:35:22.710
Just take a quick look.

00:35:32.710 --> 00:35:33.760
You know,

00:35:34.510 --> 00:35:35.800
I once had a little sister.

00:35:37.710 --> 00:35:39.000
If she were still with us today,

00:35:40.550 --> 00:35:41.800
she'd be about your age.

00:35:46.360 --> 00:35:47.360
I've seen her.

00:35:52.590 --> 00:35:53.150
Mom?

00:35:54.590 --> 00:35:55.840
Mom, you okay?

00:35:59.030 --> 00:35:59.800
It's fine, Dad.

00:36:00.320 --> 00:36:01.150
Didn't hit Mom's feet.

00:36:01.920 --> 00:36:02.710
We're all busy here.

00:36:03.030 --> 00:36:03.880
What's the matter?

00:36:04.150 --> 00:36:05.280
Nothing, Sanjin.

00:36:05.710 --> 00:36:06.840
Keep working.

00:36:06.840 --> 00:36:07.880
We just came to check.

00:36:10.320 --> 00:36:11.190
This is the one...

00:36:12.030 --> 00:36:13.000
The girl we left

00:36:13.480 --> 00:36:14.630
in town back then.

00:36:34.710 --> 00:36:36.320
You're my eldest sister.

00:36:43.280 --> 00:36:43.800
Mom...

00:36:45.280 --> 00:36:46.960
Mom? Mom!

00:36:48.000 --> 00:36:48.920
Calm down, Mom.

00:36:49.440 --> 00:36:50.920
My sister's back!

00:36:51.670 --> 00:36:53.280
My sister's back!

00:36:58.190 --> 00:36:59.030
Calm down now.

00:37:00.920 --> 00:37:02.440
Don't go near her! She's sick!

00:37:02.550 --> 00:37:03.400
She might hurt you!

00:37:04.480 --> 00:37:05.230
Mr. He?

00:37:06.000 --> 00:37:06.710
Don't you know

00:37:06.710 --> 00:37:07.590
your daughter's sick?

00:37:09.030 --> 00:37:09.880
Bringing someone here,

00:37:10.150 --> 00:37:11.360
you should give us a heads-up.

00:37:11.630 --> 00:37:12.760
If her condition gets worse,

00:37:13.070 --> 00:37:14.110
how can we build the house?

00:37:15.440 --> 00:37:16.030
Oh, well...

00:37:16.550 --> 00:37:17.400
You've seen her.

00:37:17.960 --> 00:37:18.550
Let's go back.

00:37:21.630 --> 00:37:22.960
This is not the time...

00:37:36.920 --> 00:37:37.510
You see...

00:37:38.070 --> 00:37:39.670
It's the busiest day for us.

00:37:40.360 --> 00:37:41.150
I'm sorry.

00:37:41.920 --> 00:37:42.590
Maybe...

00:37:43.150 --> 00:37:44.320
Come back next time.

00:37:55.760 --> 00:37:56.760
How did she get sick?

00:37:57.190 --> 00:37:57.840
Stop asking.

00:37:58.320 --> 00:37:59.230
I need to ask.

00:38:02.670 --> 00:38:03.400
It's my fault.

00:38:04.440 --> 00:38:05.150
And yours, too.

00:38:05.840 --> 00:38:07.110
Why is it my fault?

00:38:09.710 --> 00:38:12.190
Back when Xiaoqin was 19,

00:38:12.360 --> 00:38:13.710
she was engaged to a young man

00:38:13.710 --> 00:38:14.480
from the city.

00:38:14.590 --> 00:38:16.110
He wanted a dowry before moving

00:38:16.670 --> 00:38:17.630
to the countryside.

00:38:18.030 --> 00:38:19.150
But I was poor.

00:38:19.550 --> 00:38:20.880
I was reluctant to spend money.

00:38:21.280 --> 00:38:22.800
But at that time, my wife

00:38:23.150 --> 00:38:24.630
went into premature labor.

00:38:25.150 --> 00:38:25.880
I was terrified.

00:38:26.230 --> 00:38:26.840
A premature labor

00:38:26.960 --> 00:38:28.920
means it's probably a girl.

00:38:29.840 --> 00:38:31.760
So I took some money and went

00:38:31.880 --> 00:38:33.400
to the fortuneteller, trying

00:38:33.480 --> 00:38:34.320
to change your fate.

00:38:35.150 --> 00:38:37.110
But he'd been arrested

00:38:37.360 --> 00:38:38.440
for fraud

00:38:38.590 --> 00:38:40.030
and was being punished.

00:38:40.590 --> 00:38:42.230
We were afraid to get involved,

00:38:42.230 --> 00:38:43.110
so we ran off.

00:38:43.280 --> 00:38:44.320
But on the way,

00:38:44.480 --> 00:38:45.590
you were born.

00:38:46.510 --> 00:38:48.150
If we hadn't met Ms. Fang,

00:38:48.960 --> 00:38:50.030
the one who gave birth to you

00:38:50.510 --> 00:38:51.480
would have been...

00:38:53.030 --> 00:38:53.710
My real mother...

00:38:53.920 --> 00:38:55.510
Oh, don't say that!

00:38:56.480 --> 00:38:58.030
Ms. Fang raised you

00:38:58.030 --> 00:38:59.030
to this age.

00:38:59.070 --> 00:39:00.280
She must have spent

00:39:00.320 --> 00:39:01.550
so much money and effort.

00:39:02.360 --> 00:39:03.760
Do you know what this is called?

00:39:04.760 --> 00:39:05.670
It's called fate!

00:39:06.070 --> 00:39:07.760
You can't change your fate.

00:39:08.840 --> 00:39:09.590
Besides,

00:39:10.150 --> 00:39:11.110
Shenxian Peak

00:39:11.800 --> 00:39:13.550
doesn't lack a woman like you.

00:39:16.670 --> 00:39:19.000
Your mother's name is He Hua.

00:39:19.280 --> 00:39:20.960
On the way back after giving birth,

00:39:21.510 --> 00:39:22.760
the rain triggered her condition.

00:39:23.440 --> 00:39:24.710
She had a seizure.

00:39:26.960 --> 00:39:29.070
Even with all the treatment,

00:39:29.150 --> 00:39:31.670
all the money spent,
and all the debts owed,

00:39:33.000 --> 00:39:34.360
she didn't survive.

00:39:34.630 --> 00:39:35.550
Later,

00:39:35.800 --> 00:39:37.480
that young man from the city

00:39:38.550 --> 00:39:40.030
saw my family's situation

00:39:40.670 --> 00:39:41.840
and broke the engagement.

00:39:43.150 --> 00:39:44.800
So my eldest sister
is sick because of that?

00:39:45.230 --> 00:39:46.150
They said

00:39:46.960 --> 00:39:48.000
she was traumatized.

00:39:48.360 --> 00:39:49.360
She couldn't stop

00:39:49.360 --> 00:39:50.550
yelling and crying

00:39:50.590 --> 00:39:51.440
when she saw us

00:39:51.440 --> 00:39:52.840
come back without you.

00:39:52.880 --> 00:39:54.510
There was simply no way
to calm her down.

00:39:55.400 --> 00:39:57.480
She even sneaked into town

00:39:57.480 --> 00:39:58.760
a couple of times,

00:39:59.190 --> 00:40:00.400
trying to find you,

00:40:01.030 --> 00:40:01.920
her youngest sister.

00:40:04.400 --> 00:40:05.510
She went looking for me?

00:40:07.670 --> 00:40:08.670
It's been years.

00:40:09.320 --> 00:40:09.880
It's all

00:40:09.880 --> 00:40:11.840
in the past now.

00:40:13.110 --> 00:40:14.510
Let's not talk about it.

00:40:31.710 --> 00:40:32.320
See?

00:40:33.000 --> 00:40:34.070
They're butchering the pig.

00:40:34.440 --> 00:40:35.480
Let's not go inside.

00:40:40.760 --> 00:40:41.320
Hey!

00:40:43.110 --> 00:40:44.670
This is the girl

00:40:45.030 --> 00:40:46.510
we left in town.

00:40:48.000 --> 00:40:49.510
Ms. Fang's daughter.

00:40:51.670 --> 00:40:52.760
Oh, my sister?

00:40:54.030 --> 00:40:55.710
So you're my sister!

00:40:58.070 --> 00:40:59.550
I'm making pig blood tofu.

00:41:00.000 --> 00:41:01.630
My clothes are all stained.

00:41:01.630 --> 00:41:02.550
I can't hug you.

00:41:04.230 --> 00:41:04.880
Alright, then.

00:41:06.110 --> 00:41:07.440
You've seen the two you wanted to see.

00:41:07.880 --> 00:41:09.320
I'll go back to dry the chili peppers.

00:41:09.400 --> 00:41:10.630
Merchants are coming soon.

00:41:11.150 --> 00:41:11.840
Aren't you leaving?

00:41:15.070 --> 00:41:15.840
Then I'll go.

00:41:21.800 --> 00:41:22.670
Zhao Kai!

00:41:22.710 --> 00:41:24.000
Come and take your dog away!

00:41:26.590 --> 00:41:27.590
Why are you barking?

00:41:27.840 --> 00:41:29.190
You're such an annoying dog!

00:41:29.320 --> 00:41:30.550
Why do you yell at him?

00:41:30.550 --> 00:41:31.760
Just take him away.

00:41:33.280 --> 00:41:34.230
It's okay, don't worry.

00:41:36.230 --> 00:41:37.360
That's my son,

00:41:37.840 --> 00:41:38.510
your nephew.

00:41:39.280 --> 00:41:40.480
He's in junior high now.

00:41:41.480 --> 00:41:42.510
Son, who is it?

00:41:42.880 --> 00:41:43.510
I don't know.

00:41:43.840 --> 00:41:44.440
A woman.

00:41:44.920 --> 00:41:46.230
Looks like she's from the city.

00:41:46.510 --> 00:41:47.150
Empty-handed.

00:41:47.630 --> 00:41:48.280
Empty-handed?

00:41:49.070 --> 00:41:49.880
From the city?

00:41:50.550 --> 00:41:51.360
Hey, keep playing!

00:41:52.920 --> 00:41:53.480
Hurry up!

00:41:53.480 --> 00:41:54.070
Xiaoju!

00:41:54.110 --> 00:41:55.030
Don't forget to cook!

00:41:55.230 --> 00:41:55.710
Okay!

00:41:57.630 --> 00:41:59.000
We have guests here.

00:41:59.230 --> 00:42:00.280
I can't invite you

00:42:00.280 --> 00:42:01.280
into the house.

00:42:01.800 --> 00:42:02.800
Well, then...

00:42:03.000 --> 00:42:04.360
You go ahead. I'll leave now.

00:42:05.070 --> 00:42:06.070
Hey, let's talk more.

00:42:06.480 --> 00:42:07.360
Is your dad

00:42:07.360 --> 00:42:08.590
still the county head?

00:42:09.320 --> 00:42:11.030
And has your mom,
the school principal,

00:42:11.030 --> 00:42:11.710
already retired?

00:42:15.400 --> 00:42:16.280
They're doing well.

00:42:17.550 --> 00:42:19.510
You... You have a niece, too.

00:42:20.150 --> 00:42:21.190
She's working

00:42:21.190 --> 00:42:22.400
in Yu County now.

00:42:22.630 --> 00:42:23.760
But jobs are hard to find.

00:42:23.760 --> 00:42:25.360
She's doing all kinds
of part‑time jobs.

00:42:25.510 --> 00:42:26.070
You see,

00:42:26.630 --> 00:42:27.440
could you please

00:42:27.440 --> 00:42:28.590
ask your dad and mom

00:42:28.590 --> 00:42:29.840
to help her

00:42:29.840 --> 00:42:31.320
find a stable job?

00:42:33.960 --> 00:42:34.550
I'm leaving.

00:42:35.590 --> 00:42:37.150
Hey... Give me your address.

00:42:37.150 --> 00:42:38.360
Where should I find you?

00:42:39.440 --> 00:42:40.630
Guiyang Normal University,

00:42:41.150 --> 00:42:41.920
Chinese Department.

00:42:43.630 --> 00:42:44.760
Hey, your niece's name

00:42:44.800 --> 00:42:45.920
is Zhao Jun!

00:42:46.000 --> 00:42:47.360
If she comes to you in the city,

00:42:47.480 --> 00:42:48.630
be nice to her!

00:42:48.710 --> 00:42:49.840
You're the only upper-class

00:42:49.840 --> 00:42:51.110
relative we have!

00:42:51.230 --> 00:42:53.000
Just give her a hand!